pve-fclu (0.1.0~alpha15) stable; urgency=medium

  * hitachi: correct the qm-clone host-mapping fix (alpha14's single /host-wwns query
    is rejected by CM REST, which requires hostGroupNumber). publish_lu now resolves
    each port's host group by the name ensure_host_access already found (cached
    host-group list) instead of re-scanning WWNs per group — eliminates the ~90
    REST queries/clone. list_host_groups cache gains a 30s TTL.

